{
  "openapi": "3.0.3",
  "info": {
    "title": "SnapPath AI Brain API",
    "version": "1.1.0",
    "description": "SnapPath API service documentation untuk client terdaftar. Client eksternal memakai x-api-key dan x-api-secret, sedangkan dashboard internal SnapPath memakai JWT session user login."
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "http://localhost:3000",
      "description": "Local development server"
    }
  ],
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "Clinical Pathway Result Guide",
      "description": "Panduan membaca setiap section hasil Clinical Pathway di dashboard SnapPath."
    },
    {
      "name": "Authentication",
      "description": "Client eksternal memakai x-api-key + x-api-secret atau Basic auth. Dashboard SnapPath memakai JWT session internal."
    },
    {
      "name": "Claim Workflows",
      "description": "Workflow validasi klaim end-to-end dan polling result."
    },
    {
      "name": "Clinical Pathway",
      "description": "Generate dan interpretasi clinical pathway AI."
    },
    {
      "name": "Tariff",
      "description": "Master tarif dan validasi harga tindakan."
    },
    {
      "name": "Drug Price",
      "description": "Validasi harga obat dengan cache dan AI-assisted market reference."
    },
    {
      "name": "Providers",
      "description": "Provider klaim/tarif milik client, misalnya BPJS atau private insurer."
    },
    {
      "name": "Jobs",
      "description": "Polling status dan result job asynchronous."
    }
  ],
  "components": {
    "securitySchemes": {
      "ApiKeyAuth": {
        "type": "apiKey",
        "in": "header",
        "name": "x-api-key",
        "description": "Public API key client, contoh: sp_xxx"
      },
      "ApiSecretAuth": {
        "type": "apiKey",
        "in": "header",
        "name": "x-api-secret",
        "description": "API secret client, contoh: sps_xxx"
      },
      "BasicAuth": {
        "type": "http",
        "scheme": "basic",
        "description": "Alternative auth: Authorization Basic base64(apiKey:apiSecret)"
      }
    },
    "schemas": {
      "ErrorResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "error": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      },
      "QueuedJobResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "success": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "example": true
          },
          "jobId": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "uuid"
          },
          "runId": {
            "type": "string",
            "nullable": true
          },
          "message": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "statusUrl": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "/api/v1/jobs/{jobId}/status"
          }
        }
      },
      "ClaimValidationInput": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "providerId",
          "patient",
          "encounter",
          "diagnoses",
          "procedures",
          "medications",
          "totalClaimAmount"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "clientId": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "uuid",
            "nullable": true,
            "description": "Optional. Jika memakai API key client, clientId otomatis diambil dari credential."
          },
          "providerId": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "uuid",
            "description": "Provider klaim/tarif yang digunakan untuk threshold dan master tariff."
          },
          "claimId": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "CLM-2026-0001"
          },
          "patient": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Patient"
          },
          "encounter": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Encounter"
          },
          "diagnoses": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Diagnosis"
            }
          },
          "procedures": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Procedure"
            }
          },
          "medications": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Medication"
            }
          },
          "documents": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ClinicalDocument"
            }
          },
          "totalClaimAmount": {
            "type": "number",
            "example": 3250000
          },
          "currency": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "IDR"
          },
          "notes": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      },
      "Patient": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "P-001"
          },
          "name": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "Budi Santoso"
          },
          "dateOfBirth": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "date",
            "example": "1985-04-21"
          },
          "gender": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "M",
              "F"
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "Encounter": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "type": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "RAWAT_INAP",
              "RAWAT_JALAN",
              "IGD"
            ]
          },
          "admissionDate": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "date-time"
          },
          "dischargeDate": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "date-time",
            "nullable": true
          },
          "facility": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "id": {
                "type": "string"
              },
              "name": {
                "type": "string"
              },
              "type": {
                "type": "string",
                "example": "RS_TIPE_B"
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "Diagnosis": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "code": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "J18.9"
          },
          "description": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "Pneumonia, unspecified organism"
          },
          "type": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "PRIMARY",
              "SECONDARY",
              "COMPLICATION"
            ]
          },
          "sequence": {
            "type": "integer",
            "example": 1
          }
        }
      },
      "Procedure": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "code": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "RAD-CXR"
          },
          "description": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "Chest X-Ray"
          },
          "quantity": {
            "type": "integer",
            "example": 1
          },
          "unitPrice": {
            "type": "number",
            "example": 250000
          },
          "totalPrice": {
            "type": "number",
            "example": 250000
          },
          "performedDate": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "date-time"
          },
          "category": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "RADIOLOGI"
          },
          "regionCode": {
            "type": "string",
            "nullable": true
          }
        }
      },
      "Medication": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "name": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "Azithromycin 500mg"
          },
          "genericName": {
            "type": "string",
            "nullable": true
          },
          "dosage": {
            "type": "string",
            "nullable": true
          },
          "quantity": {
            "type": "integer",
            "example": 5
          },
          "unitPrice": {
            "type": "number",
            "example": 15000
          },
          "totalPrice": {
            "type": "number",
            "example": 75000
          },
          "frequency": {
            "type": "string",
            "nullable": true
          },
          "duration": {
            "type": "string",
            "nullable": true
          }
        }
      },
      "ClinicalDocument": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "type": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "KTP",
            "enum": [
              "LMA",
              "KTP",
              "KARTU ASURANSI",
              "SK KAMAR",
              "FORM KRONOLOGIS KECELAKAAN",
              "SURAT PERNYATAAN RAWAT INAP"
            ]
          },
          "url": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "uri"
          },
          "description": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      },
      "ClinicalPathwayInput": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "diagnosisCode",
          "encounterType"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "clientId": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "uuid",
            "nullable": true
          },
          "providerId": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "uuid",
            "nullable": true
          },
          "diagnosisCode": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "A09"
          },
          "diagnosisName": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "Infectious gastroenteritis and colitis"
          },
          "encounterType": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "RAWAT_INAP",
              "RAWAT_JALAN",
              "IGD"
            ]
          },
          "providerType": {
            "type": "string",
            "nullable": true,
            "example": "BPJS"
          },
          "patientProfile": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "age": {
                "type": "integer"
              },
              "gender": {
                "type": "string",
                "enum": [
                  "M",
                  "F"
                ]
              },
              "comorbidities": {
                "type": "array",
                "items": {
                  "type": "string"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "includeCosting": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "default": false
          }
        }
      },
      "ClinicalPathwayOutput": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Core result clinical pathway. Jika dipanggil via /pathways/generate, result ini tersedia di GET /api/v1/jobs/{jobId}/result pada field result.",
        "properties": {
          "jobId": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "uuid"
          },
          "diagnosisCode": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "A09"
          },
          "diagnosisName": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "pathwayVersion": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "1.0-ai"
          },
          "estimatedLos": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "Perkiraan Length of Stay standar dalam hari."
          },
          "phases": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ClinicalPathwayPhase"
            }
          },
          "totalEstimatedCost": {
            "type": "number",
            "nullable": true
          },
          "generatedBy": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "AI",
              "TEMPLATE",
              "HYBRID"
            ]
          },
          "confidence": {
            "type": "number",
            "description": "Confidence internal terhadap pathway yang dihasilkan."
          }
        }
      },
      "ClinicalPathwayPhase": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Satu fase perjalanan perawatan. Phase biasanya Admission/IGD, Day 1-2, Day 3-5, Discharge.",
        "properties": {
          "phaseId": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "admission"
          },
          "phaseName": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "IGD/Admisi"
          },
          "dayRange": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "Day 0"
          },
          "objectives": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "description": "Target klinis fase ini."
          },
          "assessments": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/PathwayAssessment"
            }
          },
          "treatments": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/PathwayTreatment"
            }
          },
          "medications": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/PathwayMedication"
            }
          },
          "nursing": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/PathwayNursing"
            }
          },
          "nutrition": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/PathwayNutrition"
          },
          "education": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          "dischargeGate": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/DischargeGate"
          }
        }
      },
      "PathwayAssessment": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "name": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "frequency": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "mandatory": {
            "type": "boolean"
          }
        }
      },
      "PathwayTreatment": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "name": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "route": {
            "type": "string",
            "nullable": true
          },
          "mandatory": {
            "type": "boolean"
          }
        }
      },
      "PathwayMedication": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "name": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "dosage": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "frequency": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "route": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "duration": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "mandatory": {
            "type": "boolean"
          }
        }
      },
      "PathwayNursing": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "activity": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "frequency": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      },
      "PathwayNutrition": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "diet": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "restrictions": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "nullable": true
          }
        }
      },
      "DischargeGate": {
        "type": "object",
        "nullable": true,
        "properties": {
          "criteria": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          "mustMeetAll": {
            "type": "boolean"
          }
        }
      },
      "ClaimValidationOutput": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "jobId": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "status": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "VALID",
              "INVALID",
              "WARNING",
              "REVIEW_NEEDED"
            ]
          },
          "overallScore": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "Skor akhir 0-100 setelah scoring deduction."
          },
          "summary": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "scoringExplanation": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ScoringExplanation"
          },
          "documentValidation": {
            "type": "object"
          },
          "diagnosisValidation": {
            "type": "object"
          },
          "tariffValidation": {
            "type": "object"
          },
          "drugPriceValidation": {
            "type": "object"
          },
          "clinicalPathway": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ClaimClinicalPathwaySection"
          },
          "processingTime": {
            "type": "object"
          },
          "auditTrail": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "object"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "ScoringExplanation": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Penjelasan scoring yang digunakan di SnapPath UI. Skor dimulai dari 100 lalu dikurangi berdasarkan temuan validasi.",
        "properties": {
          "baseScore": {
            "type": "integer",
            "example": 100
          },
          "deductions": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "parameter": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "example": "Diagnosis & tindakan klinis"
                },
                "maxDeduction": {
                  "type": "integer",
                  "example": 30
                },
                "trigger": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "example": "diagnosisValidation.isValid === false"
                },
                "meaning": {
                  "type": "string"
                }
              }
            },
            "example": [
              {
                "parameter": "Diagnosis & tindakan klinis",
                "maxDeduction": 30,
                "trigger": "Diagnosis tidak sesuai tindakan atau prosedur wajib hilang",
                "meaning": "Mendeteksi mismatch diagnosis-treatment, prosedur tidak relevan, atau prosedur wajib belum ada."
              },
              {
                "parameter": "Tarif tindakan",
                "maxDeduction": 20,
                "trigger": "tariffValidation.status WARNING/INVALID",
                "meaning": "Ada item tarif di luar master tariff atau melewati threshold."
              },
              {
                "parameter": "Harga obat",
                "maxDeduction": 20,
                "trigger": "drugPriceValidation.status WARNING/INVALID",
                "meaning": "Harga obat melewati referensi pasar + threshold atau obat tidak ditemukan."
              },
              {
                "parameter": "Kelengkapan dokumen",
                "maxDeduction": 10,
                "trigger": "documentValidation.isValid === false",
                "meaning": "Dokumen mandatory LMA, KTP, Kartu Asuransi, SK Kamar, Form Kronologis Kecelakaan, dan Surat Pernyataan Rawat Inap belum lengkap."
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "ClaimClinicalPathwaySection": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Section clinicalPathway di full claim validation. Berisi recommendedPathway hasil AI/template untuk diagnosis primer.",
        "properties": {
          "diagnosisCode": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "adherenceScore": {
            "type": "integer",
            "example": 100,
            "description": "Saat ini default 100 karena sistem menghasilkan pathway rekomendasi; deviasi detail akan diisi saat adherence engine aktif."
          },
          "recommendedPathway": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ClinicalPathwayPhase"
            }
          },
          "deviations": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "TariffEntry": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "providerId": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "procedureCode": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "procedureName": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "category": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "subcategory": {
            "type": "string",
            "nullable": true
          },
          "serviceCode": {
            "type": "string",
            "nullable": true
          },
          "unit": {
            "type": "string",
            "nullable": true
          },
          "regionCode": {
            "type": "string",
            "nullable": true
          },
          "basePrice": {
            "type": "number"
          },
          "maxPrice": {
            "type": "number"
          },
          "priceTiersJson": {
            "type": "object",
            "nullable": true
          },
          "currency": {
            "type": "string",
            "default": "IDR"
          },
          "notes": {
            "type": "string",
            "nullable": true
          },
          "effectiveFrom": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "date-time"
          },
          "effectiveTo": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "date-time",
            "nullable": true
          },
          "isActive": {
            "type": "boolean"
          }
        }
      },
      "ProviderInput": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "code",
          "name"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "clientId": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "uuid",
            "nullable": true
          },
          "code": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "BPJS"
          },
          "name": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "BPJS Kesehatan"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "security": [
    {
      "ApiKeyAuth": [],
      "ApiSecretAuth": []
    },
    {
      "BasicAuth": []
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/guide/clinical-pathway-result/ai-outcome-summary": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "Clinical Pathway Result Guide"
        ],
        "summary": "Guide: AI Outcome & Validation Summary",
        "description": "Section ini adalah ringkasan paling atas dari hasil clinical pathway dan validasi klaim.\n\n| Item | Penjelasan |\n| --- | --- |\n| Overall Score | Skor akhir 0-100. Skor awal 100 lalu dikurangi berdasarkan issue validasi. |\n| Status Validasi | Valid, Warning, Review Needed, atau Invalid sebagai indikator risiko review. |\n| Perhitungan Skor | Breakdown pengurangan skor dari diagnosis, tarif tindakan, harga obat, dokumen, LOS compliance, dan master data tidak terdaftar. |\n| Validasi Obat & Tindakan | Persentase item yang sesuai dari total validasi tarif, obat, dan diagnosis-treatment. |\n| Length of Stay (LOS compliance) | Membandingkan LOS compliance aktual dengan standar LOS compliance dari AI pathway. Jika overstay, masuk pengurangan skor. |\n| Kelengkapan Dokumen Medis | Jumlah dokumen tersedia dan dokumen wajib yang hilang. |\n| Catatan Varians & Outcome | Catatan tambahan dari input user untuk menjelaskan variance atau outcome klinis. |\n\n\n\n**Catatan interpretasi**\n\n- `Tarif tindakan terdaftar` dan `Harga obat terdaftar` hanya menilai item yang sudah memiliki referensi harga.\n- Jika tindakan/obat belum punya referensi, deduction masuk ke `Kesiapan master data`, bukan ke price compliance.\n- `LOS compliance` berdiri sendiri dan hanya minus jika LOS aktual melebihi standar pathway.\n\n**Preview section**\n\n```text\nAI Outcome & Validation Summary        [Valid]\n\nScore Count\nAwal 100 | Minus -20 | Akhir 80\n\n- Diagnosis & tindakan klinis   0 / 30\n- Tarif tindakan terdaftar              -20 / 20\n- Harga obat terdaftar                    0 / 20\n- Kelengkapan dokumen           0 / 10\n- LOS compliance                            0 / 10\n- Kesiapan master data    0 / 15\n\nConformance Metrics\n- Validasi Obat & Tindakan: 86% Sesuai\n- LOS compliance: 3 hari aktual - standar AI 3 hari\n- Dokumen: 6 dokumen wajib dilampirkan\n```\n\n> Catatan: path guide ini adalah dokumentasi konseptual di API Docs, bukan endpoint runtime.",
        "security": [],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Documentation only. Not a runtime API endpoint."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/guide/clinical-pathway-result/patient-clinical-summary": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "Clinical Pathway Result Guide"
        ],
        "summary": "Guide: Patient Clinical Summary",
        "description": "Section ini merangkum konteks pasien dan episode perawatan agar reviewer tidak perlu membaca payload mentah.\n\n| Item | Penjelasan |\n| --- | --- |\n| Patient Identity | Nama pasien, gender/tanggal lahir, MRN, dan nomor asuransi bila tersedia. |\n| Admission Episode | Tipe encounter, tanggal masuk, tanggal pulang, dan LOS aktual. |\n| Diagnoses | Daftar diagnosis primary/secondary/complication beserta kode dan deskripsi. |\n| AI Clinical Context | Ringkasan klinis singkat dari AI untuk diagnosis utama. |\n| Procedures Claimed | Ringkasan tindakan yang diklaim, biasanya menampilkan kode dan nama tindakan. |\n| Medications Claimed | Ringkasan obat yang diklaim, termasuk nama dan jumlah. |\n\n**Preview section**\n\n```text\nPatient Clinical Summary\n\nPatient Identity\nName        Budi Santoso\nGender/DOB  M - 21 Apr 1985\nMRN         MR-001\nInsurance   BPJS-00001\n\nAdmission Episode\nType        RAWAT_INAP\nAdmission   20 Mei 2026\nDischarge   23 Mei 2026\nLOS         3 Days (AI Standard: 3 days)\n\nDiagnoses\n[J18.9] Pneumonia (primary)\n\nAI Clinical Context\nRingkasan kondisi klinis utama pasien.\n```\n\n> Catatan: path guide ini adalah dokumentasi konseptual di API Docs, bukan endpoint runtime.",
